The Guidelines & Policies section contains prompts for establishing clear ethical frameworks, client agreements, and quality standards for your AI creative work. These templates help you articulate your approach to transparency, ownership, privacy, and quality assurance. Use these when developing client contracts, website content explaining your process, or internal guidelines for your own practice. They're essential for building trust, setting appropriate expectations, and ensuring consistency in how you approach important aspects of your business.
